<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<h2 id="head-803eea3bed91671ad3d3c9f76dbc0dedaf21a9e5">The Harp of Maglor</h2>
<em>This harp that once belonged to Maglor makes those who use it seem more forceful and convincing. It is also said that those who have used it found themselves walking faster, as if to an unheard beat.</em> <p>
It increases your wisdom, charisma, stealth, speed and luck by 3. It provides resistance to acid, electricity, fire, cold and sound. It allows you to see invisible monsters. It allows you to sense the presence of unique beings. 
</p>
